column2: ggplot(arnold_data_endo, aes(y = Zr, x = Year, size = 1/sqrt(Zr_v))) + geom_point(alpha = 0.30) + geom_smooth(method = lm, col = "red", show.legend = FALSE) + labs(x = "Publication Year", y = "Fisher's Z-transformed Correlation Coefficient (Zr)", size = "Precision (1/SE)") + theme_classic()
